                        <interp inst="t18470705-name-215" type="given" value="JOSEPH ROBINSON"></interp>JOSEPH ROBINSON HADFIELD.</persName>
                  </hi> I live at No.326, High Holborn—I en<lb></lb>gaged the prisoner as errand-boy. On the 9th of June, about half-past nine o'clock in the morning I sent him up to my room for a pair of trowsers—there was a watch in the room on the drawers—I went into the room at eleven o'clock; the watch was then gone—this produced is it.</p>
